{
  "page": "Mara Martell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/50px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/75px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/100px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Princess</span><br />Mara Martell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/50px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/75px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/100px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Princess of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_Sunspear\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady of Sunspear\">Lady of Sunspear</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/83_AC\" title=\"83 AC\">83</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Mara Nymeros Martell</b> was the ruling <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a> and head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mara_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Mara became the ruling Princess of Dorne in <a href=\"/index.php/83_AC\" title=\"83 AC\">83&#160;AC</a> after the death of Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Morion_Martell\" title=\"Morion Martell\">Morion Martell</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Fourth_Dornish_War\" title=\"Fourth Dornish War\">Fourth Dornish War</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mara_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Her relation to her predecessor, <a href=\"/index.php/Morion_Martell\" title=\"Morion Martell\">Morion Martell</a>, is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mara_Martell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Long Reign - Jaehaerys and Alysanne: Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Morion_Martell\" title=\"Morion Martell\">Morion Martell</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Princess of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_Sunspear\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady of Sunspear\">Lady of Sunspear</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/83_AC\" title=\"83 AC\">83&#160;AC</a>–?\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren Martell</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist mw-collapsible mw-collapsed collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Princes_of_Dorne\" title=\"Template:Princes of Dorne\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Princes_of_Dorne&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Princes of Dorne (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Princes_of_Dorne&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Princes and Princesses of Dorne</a> since <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Aegon's Conquest</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Meria_Martell\" title=\"Meria Martell\">Meria Martell</a> (~62 BC-13 AC)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nymor_Martell\" title=\"Nymor Martell\">Nymor Martell</a> (13-?)<sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Deria_Martell\" title=\"Deria Martell\">Deria Martell</a><sup>1,2</sup></li>\n<li>Unknown<sup>2</sup></li>\n<li>Morion's father<sup>3</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Morion_Martell\" title=\"Morion Martell\">Morion Martell</a> (?-83)</li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mara Martell</a> (83-?)<sup>4</sup></li>\n<li>Unknown<sup>4</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qoren_Martell\" title=\"Qoren Martell\">Qoren Martell</a> (?-~132)<sup>5</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aliandra_Martell\" title=\"Aliandra Martell\">Aliandra Martell</a> (~132-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne_(father_of_Maron)\" title=\"Prince of Dorne (father of Maron)\">Maron's father</a><sup>6</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maron_Martell\" title=\"Maron Martell\">Maron Martell</a><sup>7</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maron_Martell%27s_son\" title=\"Maron Martell&#39;s son\">Maron's son</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne_(mother_of_Doran)\" title=\"Princess of Dorne (mother of Doran)\">Doran's mother</a> (?-279/280)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a> (279/280—)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<ul><li><sup>1</sup> Deria is known to have succeeded her father Nymor as the ruler of Dorne by <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_23_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">23&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>2</sup> An unknown Prince of Dorne ruled in <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a> and sent his sister to the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">Golden Wedding</a></li>\n<li><sup>3</sup> Known to have ruled Dorne in <a href=\"/index.php/61_AC\" title=\"61 AC\">61&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>4</sup> An unknown Prince of Dorne ruled in <a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101&#160;AC</a> and sent his daughter to the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Council#Great_Council_of_101_AC\" title=\"Great Council\">Great Council of 101 AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>5</sup> Known to have been ruling Dorne by <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_110_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">110&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>6</sup> Known to have been ruling Dorne by <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_157_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">157&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>7</sup> Known to have been ruling Dorne by <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_174_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">174&#160;AC</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403231826\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.090 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.301 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1198/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 20520/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 19196/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 5512/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 831/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.59 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  287.323      1 -total\n 79.38%  228.063      1 Template: